         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>The Curakurucarukkam is complete. Total tiruviruttam 832. the essence of Śiva. The
               foot of the teacher is the support. In the auspicious day when Jovian year Pārapava,
               month of Āṭi, 20th day, seventh [lunar day], Tuesday and the constellation of Cuvāti
               fall together, [personal name?] who is in the town of Putuvai.</p>
         </div>
